task.summary: Bug with game ending condition fixed

Move ordering and "opponent modelling" Implemented move ordering with very simple criteria for ordering (also probably not very efficient). Also added the opponent modelling extra bit that changes values based on moves made towards or away from revealed pieces. Also made some preparations for hopefully enabling more dynamic adaptation of AI properties (i.e. not a different class just to have iterative deepening, control whether move ordering is applied and so on).
Small updates, can choose evaluation function now
